title: 某外国电视节目中的恶搞歌曲<bye bye hua wei>
contents:
Birds are falling from the sky, 鸟儿从天上落下
We're not gonna die 我们不会挂
No, 5G's redination's nothing to fear 不，5G辐射没那么可怕
I'm texting with my bro's 我正给我的哥们发短信
While watching kees and co 同时在看kees and co
But I don't want the Chinese people to know 但我不想让中国人知道我在干啥
I'd rather have scandinavian rediation in the sky 我宁可让斯堪的纳维亚的辐射在空中飘
I'll throw my router out that door 我要把我的路由器扔出门外
Baby bye bye Hua Wei 再见华为

I want all the world to see 我想让全世界看见
You're better and you're cheaper 虽然你更好跟便宜
But you are watching me 但是你在监视我
It might sound crazy but it ain't no lie 听起来可能很疯狂，但这不是骗人的
Baby bye bye Hua Wei 再见华为

Don't want to be a fool for you 我不想再当傻瓜
We're leaving you forever now it's toedeloe! 我们将会永远离开你
Want no Chinese spies on my wifi.不想让中国人监视我的wifi
Baby bye bye Hua Wei 再见华为
